text: Atrachelus is a genus of assassin bugs in the family Reduviidae, found in the Americas. There are at least two described species in Atrachelus. ==Species== * Atrachelus cinereus (Fabricius, 1798) * Atrachelus mucosus (Champion, 1899) ==References== ==Further reading== * * * * * * * * * Category:Reduviidae
title: Atrachelus
